This paper deals with probabilistic programming and inference, which are topics commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the implementation of the proposed method in a generic probabilistic programming framework, which falls under the sub-category of programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of variance, which is a topic in statistics and data analysis (cs.DS).
